<a href=http://gameznet.com/eq/ target=_blank><font size=4 COLOR="#ffffff">0007:<b>EQ'Lizer </b></font></a>
<BR><a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/"><font size=2 color=#ffffff>http://gameznet.com/eq/</font></a><font size=2 color=#ffffff>-----06åé07ì˙(ã‡)06éû00ï™19ïb</font>
