	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>EXTENDED AFFLICTION UPDATE</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>We have updated our <a href='http://eq.crgaming.com/editorials/focus.asp'>Focus Effect Guide</a> with new information on Extended Affliction.<P> This ability not only increases the duration of DoT spells, but also increases the duration of Snare, Root, Mesmerizations, Tash's, Malo's and Slows.  Pretty much any spell with a negative effect that has a duration greater than 36 seconds can have it's overall duration increased by the use of Extended Affliction items.<P> You can see what items are currently known to have this ability <a href='http://eq.crgaming.com/viewarticle.asp?Article=4334'>here</a>. 	</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:baelish@castersrealm.com'>Baelish</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 4:57 PM EST</span></p></td>
