	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>GRAPHICAL DISPLAY PROBLEMS</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>If you are having problems with your inventory display or other graphical related issues after the patch the following advice is being given in game: <ul> Players that are experiencing inventory icon issues or garbled interface graphics should turn off the texture caching option from the front end options screen and then delete all .txc files from their EverQuest folder. </ul> If you are still having issues you can always contact the live chat technical support located <a href='http://eqlive.station.sony.com/support/tech_support.jsp' target='_blank'>here</a> between 9am and 9pm PDT. 	</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:baelish@castersrealm.com'>Baelish</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 2:33 PM EST</span></p></td>
