	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>PATCH MESSAGE</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Today's patch message is now available.<P> Included are the pet changes and focus item changes we have been informing you about over the last few days.<P> PvP Servers have had a significant change made with Golem Wands, Egg Shaped Pumice Stones and Oil of Fennin Ro now having casting times.  Costs on purchasing these items back from a vendor have also been significantly increased.  All of these items have been retroactively changed. 	</font>
