	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>REMINDER PATCH TODAY</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>A reminder there will be a patch today: <ul> On Wednesday, June 5th, at 3AM PDT, (11AM GMT) all servers will be brought down for a scheduled patch. The estimated downtime is 4 hours. <P> The EverQuest Operations Team  </ul> Even though only 4 hours has been given this is a full data patch with a number of new features.  It may take longer than the given time. 	</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:baelish@castersrealm.com'>Baelish</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 5:11 AM EST</span></p></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'>&nbsp;</td>
	<td valign='top' align='left'></td>
</tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign='top' align='left' class='news' width='90%'><p class='boldheader'>FOCUS DAY IS HERE</p><font face='verdana' size='2pt'>Rich Waters sent us in a clarification to our earlier guess work regarding what focus items will be in today's patch.<P> Here's what he had to say: <ul> Level I, II, and III focus items are all going in this patch. There will be new focus effects added for future items to use after we see how these work out. </ul> This means items will be going in today for all levels of players. <P> We have also put together a rough overview chart of how the various focus effects work.  You can access it <a href='http://eq.crgaming.com/editorials/focus.asp'>here</a>.	</font>
	<p class='newsig'><span class='newsig'>Submitted by </span><span class='newsiglink'><a class='newsiglink' href='mailto:baelish@castersrealm.com'>Baelish</a></span><span class='newsig'>, 1:12 AM EST</span></p></td>
