<p><img SRC="wand_spun.gif" height=43 width=294>
<br><b>June 6,2002</b></center>
<p>The EQ Servers are down AGAIN today it seems.  So, the site's going to be awfully slow again, sorry - I know it's annoying, but between the focus items coming in, and the servers down,  the load here is off the map.</p>
<p>I've done a fresh import of all the spell data, so focus effects should be in the <a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/spelllist.html>Spell Database</a>.</p>
<p>--Illia</p>
<center>
<p><img SRC="wand.gif" height=43 width=294>
<br><b>June 5, 2002</b></center>

<p>Today's update is a Vex Thal special courtesy of Guild Afterlife.&nbsp;
I hope you enjoy checking out some of the most uber items in the game.&nbsp;
I also put up a new poll.
<p>I'm going to be on vacation for the next ten days, so the updates will
again be done by Railus.&nbsp; Please submit new items and quests to Railus
at <a href="mailto:Railus@allakhazam.com">Railus@allakhazam.com</a>.&nbsp;
Also, if you have questions and problems regarding your account or the
site in general, please submit them to Illia at <a href="mailto:Illia@allakhazam.com">Illia@allakhazam.com</a>.&nbsp;
Illia will be checking my mail periodically, but you will likely get a
quicker response if you mail that address rather then the allakhazam@allakhazam.com
address.
<p>
<b>Update:</b>(Illia) I added a partial list of focus items up as a <a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/news/sdetail951.html?story=951>news story</a>.</p>
