<p><img SRC="wand_spun.gif" height=43 width=294>
<br><b>June 4, 2002</b></center>

<p>Here are today's updates.&nbsp; Also, for those of you who want a place
to discuss Asheron's Call 2 and Star Wars Galaxies, I updated the <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/ubbcgi/Ultimate.cgi">Ubb
Forums</a> to add in a forum for each game.&nbsp; Remember that the Ubb
forum has a separate username and password from the rest of the site.
<p><b>New Items:</b> <a href="/db/item.html?item=12411">Woven Platinum
Wristband</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12410">Hateful Heraldic
Pauldrons</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12409">Hateful Heraldic
Collar</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12408">Crimson Darkscale
Vambraces</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12407">Sceptre of the
Observers</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12403">Ice Tipped Acrylia
Arrow</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12405">Shadow Tipped Acrylia
Arrow</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12394">Crystallized Acid
Bracer</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12393">Cap of Enrapturement</a>
;
<p><b>Updated Items:</b> <a href="/db/item.html?item=3179">Unholy Coldstone</a>
;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=3532">Riles Sand Coin</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=3042">Plains
Pebble</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=2902">Heart of Ice</a> ;
