Skeleton Fist</a> ; <a href="/db/item.html?item=3125">Skeletal Finger</a>
;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=3117">A Shining Stone</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=2855">A
