<p><b>New Legends Items:</b> <a href="/db/item.html?item=12406">Mantle
of Rallos Zek</a> ;
<p><b>Updated Quests:</b>&nbsp; <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1365">Enchanter
Twilight Cap</a> ;
<center>
<p><img SRC="wand.gif" height=43 width=294>
<br><b>June 3, 2002</b></center>

<p>Phew.&nbsp; The site's running normally once again.&nbsp; We had hoped
to give you a glimpse at how nice the premium features really are, but
the load was just too much.&nbsp; We could easily handle even ten or twenty
thousand additional premium users on our server setup before upgrading,
but several hundred thousand was too much.&nbsp; I guess we shouldn't have
been surprised at that.&nbsp; If you didn't get a chance to try out the
services, remember that you get 5 days after you initially sign up to cancel
your service and receive a full refund.&nbsp; To show you how satisfied
most people are, in the nine months we've been doing this we have had only
three people ask for a refund in that 5 day period.&nbsp; So if you still
are not sure about it, but want to give the premium service a try, go ahead
and <a href="https://secure.allakhazam.com/signup.cgi">sign up</a> and
if you don't like it just <a href="mailto:allakhazam@allakhazam.com">e-mail
me</a> within 5 days of when you sign up and I will give you a full refund.
<p>Also, Alan posted on some nice changes that are being made to the pet
class.&nbsp; We posted a news story on it <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/news/sdetail943.html?story=943">here</a>.
<p><b>New Items:</b> <a href="/db/item.html?item=12392">Envenomed Mocassins</a>
;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12389">Velvet Slippers of Harmony</a>
;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12387">Gebron's Demented Cloak</a>
; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12385">Belt of Pestilence</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12382">Pants
of Enrapturement</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12374">Peridot
Encrusted Stein</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=12373">Dismal Rage
Battle Axe</a> ;
<p><b>Updated Items:</b> <a href="/db/item.html?item=7778">Malechite</a>
;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=10180">Ale</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=3272">Spiderling
Eye</a> ;&nbsp; <a href="/db/item.html?item=3138">Spiderling Silk</a> ;
