<a name="newsitem1023336882,82979,"></a> <SPAN CLASS="newstitle">Focus Item Corrections for Patch Tonight </SPAN>
<br>
 
<SPAN CLASS="newsreporter">- <a href="mailto:aurum@vaultnetwork.com" class="newsreporter"><b>Aurum</b></a> @ 9:14 PM PDT </SPAN>
<br>

<SPAN CLASS="newstext">
From the Developer's Corner:<UL>Hi all,<br><br>We got a few of our focus effects crossed up in this patch, and will be patching servers tonight at 3am PST to fix this issue. The same items will have a focus effect on them, but in some cases we assigned the wrong focus type to a given item. We'll be updating them in tonight's patch, so you might want to hold of on any expensive trades until after the patch since the effects on items may change slightly.<br><br>Thanks,<br><br>- The EverQuest Team</UL><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum1/HTML/000598.html">Click here</a> to view the original spot.
</SPAN><P><br>
<a name="newsitem1023336808,81658,"></a> <SPAN CLASS="newstitle">Poll: Your Favorite Fantasy Series?</SPAN>
<br>
 
<SPAN CLASS="newsreporter">- <a href="mailto:aurum@vaultnetwork.com" class="newsreporter"><b>Aurum</b></a> @ 9:13 PM PDT </SPAN>
